{"id": 763, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在日常生活中做过哪些有仪式感的事？", "description": "所谓仪式感就是：那些做了并没有什么意义但到某个时间节点或者某个情境下也有可能是为了自己崇高而龟毛的精神目标做出的事情。（题图来自：HELENA PEREZ GARCIA）", "record_count": 6012, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183741zTAb4tonI83Rm2KU.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-22T12:44:44Z", "options": [{"id": 43009, "content": "写日记", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434789}, {"id": 43265, "content": "如厕之前一定要确保自己衣服舒适，兜里没有硬物，检查过手纸，然后拿起手机……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127272}, {"id": 43266, "content": "贤者时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131716}, {"id": 43267, "content": "婚礼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197211}, {"id": 43012, "content": "写新年计划！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434794}, {"id": 43269, "content": "一 三 六花二元钱写下7个数字", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423374}, {"id": 43014, "content": "见到老师就问好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305232}, {"id": 74759, "content": "小时候家门钥匙不好拧，要嚼着泡泡糖虔诚地念“比巴卜超人给我力量！\"然后再拧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598592}, {"id": 43015, "content": " 玩木头之前，洗漱，焚香～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214454}, {"id": 44551, "content": "一个人揉面包 直到出炉的那一刻", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200914mfzGjsRYZyV1cCOM.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360430}, {"id": 43017, "content": "制定计划", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434906}, {"id": 43018, "content": "看到11:11/12:12之类的时间，截个屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431385}, {"id": 43020, "content": "外面吃饭，要洗过碗筷茶杯再用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372989}, {"id": 43021, "content": "开车在路上  和其他车子一起停在停车线之后慢慢等待倒计时的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94983}, {"id": 43277, "content": "出门时默念:钱包钥匙手机，然后昂首挺胸出门面对世界?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436448}, {"id": 43022, "content": "ML后，抽口烟纪念下！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434925}, {"id": 43023, "content": "从生日前几天就开始筹划，接到到了当天发现没什么特别的事情发生。还有就是从小学参加各种冬夏令营，为了去数码世界，一直等到了大学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233183}, {"id": 43024, "content": "在外面餐馆吃完饭，把自己的那一小方桌子收拾干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242614}, {"id": 44304, "content": "參加一個朋友的party, 除了那個朋友誰都不認識。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200907Hpl5Nq364nFs9vJx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 442029}, {"id": 43025, "content": "哈哈哈哈，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434266}, {"id": 43793, "content": "看自己喜欢的电视剧电影之前，洗好澡刷好牙铺好床，舒舒服服之后，正式点开播放键。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414485}, {"id": 44305, "content": "參加一個朋友的party, 除了那個朋友誰都不認識。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200908E8kOtalcCIz9ufhm.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 442029}, {"id": 43026, "content": "输入用户名和密码！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188255}, {"id": 44306, "content": "參加一個朋友的party, 除了那個朋友別人誰都不認識。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 442029}, {"id": 43027, "content": "吃到好吃的看到造型很nice的东西一律拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433274}, {"id": 44307, "content": "考试之前焚香沐浴更衣剪头发（然而还是没有过）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440978}, {"id": 43028, "content": "给自己过生日，不管多困也要守夜到12点，然后在微博上对自己说一句“生日快乐。”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433419}, {"id": 43796, "content": "突然间多穿了一件", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437705}, {"id": 43029, "content": "月初综合症，每个月都有那么几天………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145677}, {"id": 43030, "content": "每年圣诞前夕就开始去星巴克买用红纸杯装的太妃榛果拿铁喝。☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414097}, {"id": 43031, "content": "睡觉前洗手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435010}, {"id": 43032, "content": "数码产品开盒前洗手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026}, {"id": 43033, "content": "每天的计划和总结，然而，我就是这么不自觉，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307916}, {"id": 43034, "content": "回答问题前清一清嗓子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301540}, {"id": 43035, "content": "写字前洗澡，打扫卫生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325024}, {"id": 43291, "content": "抹掉与一切与前任有关的痕迹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311796}, {"id": 43036, "content": "上课内心非常纠结要不要举手回答黑板上的问题，纠结了半天，别别人回答了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423196}, {"id": 43292, "content": "拆封", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384776}, {"id": 44828, "content": "新学期发新书的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446034}, {"id": 44829, "content": "换座位的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446034}, {"id": 55325, "content": "吃饭之前必须喝一口水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500374}, {"id": 43038, "content": "跑步前听跑步听的歌单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435036}, {"id": 46110, "content": "除夕看春晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 452553}, {"id": 49182, "content": "用淘宝买来的还不错的日式餐具做好一个人的晚餐，铺上格子桌布，俯拍。\r\n就像这样。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004726I3jAyUGlLKCkc6Na.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466425}, {"id": 43039, "content": "受伤了就去剪头发，以提醒自己可以重新开始", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200853gQUvqwNKfTEylP1I.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349741}, {"id": 43040, "content": "明天我要早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417375}, {"id": 43296, "content": "工作和学习前喝杯咖啡", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200855RG2CijH8f7Lsv3tW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 320073}, {"id": 43297, "content": "解：", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433400}, {"id": 60705, "content": "发誓自己要好好学习，但还是一如既往的抄答案", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 43042, "content": "没有智能机前 要去蹲厕 拿着两本杂志 脱掉裤子坐下去的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201831}]}